summary.title: Dataproc Metastore now GA
summary.summary: Dataproc Metastore services are now generally available.

2025-06-25.content:
App Hub supports resources from the following [sources](https://cloud.google.com/app-hub/docs/supported-resources) in [Preview](https://cloud.google.com/products#product-launch-stages):

* Dataproc Metastore Service
* Vertex AI Dataset
* Vertex AI Featurestore
* Vertex AI MetadataStore
* Vertex AI Model

summary.title: App Hub adds new data services
summary.summary: App Hub now supports Dataproc Metastore Service, Vertex AI Dataset, Vertex AI Featurestore, Vertex AI MetadataStore, and Vertex AI Model in preview. This feature enhances App Hub's capabilities by integrating more services.
